DESCRIPTION:If you're interested in running and hosting shows in unconventi
	onal locations\, this is the class for you! In this interactive 2-hour wor
	kshop\, students will learn the in’s and out’s of installing and programmi
	ng lights for live events outside of the venue! Participants will explore 
	areas such as installing light trees\, cable management\, programming ligh
	ts\, light design and placement\, and more. This class is great for those 
	who are interested in improving their concert lighting skills\, especially
	 for DIY shows or outdoor spaces.\n\nhttps://link.dice.fm/K5b4b779904b\n\n
