BEGIN:VEVENT
UID:gkGKnvbUKPHDeoS-KpvdK
SUMMARY:What Matters Most
DTSTAMP:20260413T010454Z
DTSTART:20260507T191500Z
DESCRIPTION:What Matters Most is Neighborhood House’s annual fundraising ev
	ent\\\, celebrating 120 years of impact in our community this year. Join N
	eighborhood House Washington for an evening of live entertainment\\\, insp
	iring speakers\\\, and a meaningful conversation about our work and vision
